comment.author: 9161595@N03
comment._content: A wrecked Albatros from Albatros-Flugzeugwerke? I almost wonder if it's the same plane as this one: [http://www.flickr.com/photos/sdasmarchives/6420844983/in/set-72157628101275589/] That one might be an Albatros C-1 or C-2: This one seems to have some of the same features — e.g. the long tail fin coming up the upper side of the fuselage — but with the front of it wrecked it's hard to be sure if it's really the same or not.
